---

<section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-20 sm:px-0 sm:py-28">
  <a href="/" class="mono text-sm text-dim hover:text-fg transition-colors">&larr; home</a>

  <div class="mt-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-light tracking-tight sm:text-3xl">Sayan Mohsin</h1>
    <p class="mt-1 text-dim">Senior Software Engineer — Building AI-native systems.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-dim leading-relaxed border-l border-line pl-5">
    <p>
      I write code that writes code. Sometimes it works on the first try. Usually it doesn't.
      That's what makes it fun.
    </p>
    <p>
      I design and build distributed systems that span the full stack — from real-time data
      pipelines with Kafka and Temporal, to AI agents that can code, review, and deploy
      themselves. I work across Rust, TypeScript, Go, and Java, shipping infrastructure
      that is as reliable as it is maintainable.
    </p>
    <p>
      I believe the best systems are simple, the best code is readable, and the best
      products ship fast without breaking.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="mono text-xs text-dim/50 tracking-[0.1em] uppercase mb-4">Skills</h2>
    <div class="space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <span class="mono text-dim/40 text-[13px]">Languages</span>
        <span class="text-dim"> &nbsp;TypeScript · Java · Python · Go · PHP</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="mono text-dim/40 text-[13px]">Frontend</span>
        <span class="text-dim"> &nbsp;React · Next.js · Angular · Vue · Vite</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="mono text-dim/40 text-[13px]">Backend</span>
        <span class="text-dim"> &nbsp;Spring · NestJS · FastAPI · Kafka · Temporal</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="mono text-dim/40 text-[13px]">Runtime</span>
        <span class="text-dim"> &nbsp;Node.js · Bun · Kubernetes · Docker · ArgoCD</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10">
    <h2 class="mono text-xs text-dim/50 tracking-[0.1em] uppercase mb-4">Current mission</h2>
    <div class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-dim">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-signal mono">></span>
        <span>Building distributed systems with Kafka &amp; Temporal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-signal mono">></span>
        <span>Designing AI agents that code, review, and deploy</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-signal mono">></span>
        <span>Shipping across full stack: backend → frontend → infra</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10">
    <h2 class="mono text-xs text-dim/50 tracking-[0.1em] uppercase mb-4">Contact</h2>
    <div class="space-y-1">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mono text-sm">
